<item>
            <title>[LU-11690] LBUG with very wide striping: lod_ea_store_resize()) ASSERTION( round &lt;= lov_mds_md_size(2000, (0x0BD30000 | 0x0BD0))</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11690</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There is an incorrect assert in lod_ea_store_resize which leads to an LBUG with very high stripe counts.&#160; (I didn&apos;t calculate precisely, but 1300 is OK and 1600 triggers the bug.)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The fix is trivial.&#160; Patch forthcoming.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
